### ping api (使用Cookie认证)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ping
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{authCookie}}

{
  "message": "hello"
}

### get credits
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/credits
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{authCookie}}

### gen image
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/demo/gen-image
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

{
  "prompt": "a beautiful girl running with 2 cats",
  "provider": "kling",
  "model": "kling-v1"
}

