### Kling 1.6 - 基础图片转视频测试
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/video-generation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "kling-1-6",
  "prompt": "Snowflakes fall as a car moves forward along the road.",
  "image_url": "https://storage.googleapis.com/falserverless/kling/kling_input.jpeg",
  "duration": "5",
  "aspect_ratio": "16:9",
  "negative_prompt": "blur, distort, and low quality",
  "cfg_scale": 0.5
}

### Kling 1.6 - 10秒竖屏视频测试
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/video-generation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "kling-1-6",
  "prompt": "A beautiful butterfly gently fluttering around flowers in a garden, creating graceful movements with its colorful wings",
  "image_url": "https://fal.media/files/elephant/8kkhB12hEZI2kkbU8pZPA_test.jpeg",
  "duration": "10",
  "aspect_ratio": "9:16",
  "negative_prompt": "static, motionless, blurry",
  "cfg_scale": 0.7
}

### Kling 1.6 - 1:1方形视频测试
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/video-generation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "kling-1-6",
  "prompt": "A cute cat playing with a ball of yarn, pouncing and rolling around playfully",
  "image_url": "https://storage.googleapis.com/falserverless/gallery/car_720p.png",
  "duration": "5",
  "aspect_ratio": "1:1",
  "negative_prompt": "aggressive, scary, dark",
