### Webhook 端点验证
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/video-generation/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

### 模拟 Webhook 回调 - 完成状态
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/video-generation/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "COMPLETED",
  "request_id": "test-request-12345",
  "response_url": "https://queue.fal.run/fal-ai/kling-video/v2/master/image-to-video/requests/test-request-12345",
  "response": {
    "video": {
      "url": "https://v3.fal.media/files/koala/test_output.mp4",
      "content_type": "video/mp4",
      "file_size": 5242880
    }
  },
  "logs": [
    {
      "timestamp": "2024-01-20T10:30:00Z",
      "message": "开始处理视频生成请求"
    },
    {
      "timestamp": "2024-01-20T10:35:00Z", 
      "message": "视频生成完成"
    }
  ],
  "metrics": {
    "inference_time": 240.5
  }
}

### 模拟 Webhook 回调 - 进行中状态
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/video-generation/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS",
  "request_id": "test-request-67890",
  "response_url": "https://queue.fal.run/fal-ai/kling-video/v1/standard/image-to-video/requests/test-request-67890",
  "progress": 45,
  "logs": [
    {
      "timestamp": "2024-01-20T10:30:00Z",
      "message": "正在生成视频帧..."
    }
  ]
}

### 模拟 Webhook 回调 - 失败状态
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/video-generation/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "FAILED",
  "request_id": "test-request-error",
  "response_url": "https://queue.fal.run/fal-ai/kling-video/v2/master/image-to-video/requests/test-request-error",
  "error": "图片格式不支持或图片损坏",
  "logs": [
    {
      "timestamp": "2024-01-20T10:30:00Z",
      "message": "开始处理视频生成请求"
    },
    {
      "timestamp": "2024-01-20T10:31:00Z",
      "message": "错误：无法解析输入图片"
    }
  ]
}

